THE MOST FANTASTIC

01:08:07.562 --> 01:08:11.032
AND UNLIKELY PREDICTION
EVER MADE BY PHYSICISTS.

01:08:14.936 --> 01:08:19.707
WORLD WAR I HAD JUST BROKEN OUT
WHEN ALBERT EINSTEIN PUBLISHES

01:08:19.707 --> 01:08:22.310
HIS GENERAL THEORY
OF RELATIVITY.

01:08:22.310 --> 01:08:24.478
AMONG THOSE FIGHTING
ON THE RUSSIAN FRONT

01:08:24.478 --> 01:08:26.519
IS A GERMAN ASTRONOMER
AND PHYSICIST

01:08:26.519 --> 01:08:28.816
NAMED KARL SCHWARZSCHILD.

01:08:28.816 --> 01:08:33.154
WITH THE WAR RAGING AROUND HIM,
SCHWARZSCHILD DISCOVERS

01:08:33.154 --> 01:08:36.624
THAT EINSTEIN'S EQUATIONS
PREDICT THE EXISTENCE

01:08:36.624 --> 01:08:39.226
OF A STAR SO UNIMAGINABLY DENSE

01:08:39.226 --> 01:08:42.263
THAT EVEN LIGHT
CANNOT ESCAPE IT.

01:08:43.998 --> 01:08:48.336
FROM THE BENDS
EINSTEIN HIS CALCULATIONS.

01:08:48.336 --> 01:08:51.806
JUST WEEKS AFTER RECEIVING
EINSTEIN'S REPLY

01:08:51.806 --> 01:08:54.408
SCHWARZSCHILD DIES
ON THE FRONT LINES.

01:08:57.783 --> 01:09:00.915
EINSTEIN MARVELS
AT SCHWARZSCHILD'S WORK.

01:09:00.915 --> 01:09:04.819
BUT HE NEVER ACCEPTS THAT
SUCH A STAR COULD REALLY EXIST.

01:09:04.819 --> 01:09:08.289
AS HE PUTS IT,
"IT JUST DOESN'T SMELL RIGHT."

01:09:17.398 --> 01:09:21.736
THROUGH THE 1960s, MOST
SCIENTISTS AGREE WITH EINSTEIN.

01:09:21.736 --> 01:09:25.206
BUT THE PUBLIC IS COMPLETELY
TAKEN WITH THE IDEA

01:09:25.206 --> 01:09:28.242
OF A DARK STAR FROM WHICH
ESCAPE IS IMPOSSIBLE

01:09:28.242 --> 01:09:31.278
WHERE TIME AND SPACE
CEASE TO EXIST.

01:09:37.351 --> 01:09:39.086
WE ARE FALLING.

01:09:39.520 --> 01:09:40.821
TOWARDS WHAT? I WONDER.

01:09:40.821 --> 01:09:43.858
ZEN, PUT FORWARD
COORDINATE 890 ON VISUAL.

01:09:43.858 --> 01:09:44.725
Zen:
CONFIRMED.

01:09:44.725 --> 01:09:47.328
Woman:
BUT THERE'S NOTHING THERE.

01:09:47.328 --> 01:09:49.497
ZEN, USE LONG-
RANGE INTENSIFIER.

01:09:51.232 --> 01:09:53.834
THREE GUESSES,
IF Y

01:09:55.136 --> 01:09:57.304
A BLACK HOLE.

01:09:57.304 --> 01:10:01.208
MY GOD, WE'RE FALLING
INTO A BLACK HOLE.

01:10:04.245 --> 01:10:06.847
Osgood:
THE EXISTENCE
OF A REAL BLACK HOLE

01:10:06.847 --> 01:10:09.884
IS ALMOST IMPOSSIBLE
FOR PHYSICISTS TO ACCEPT

01:10:09.884 --> 01:10:15.089
YET MANY HAVE TO ADMIT

01:10:15.089 --> 01:10:18.125
SHOULD ALSO CREATE BLACK HOLES.

01:10:18.125 --> 01:10:23.330
WHEN A STAR HAS BURNED UP
ALL ITS NUCLEAR FUEL

01:10:23.330 --> 01:10:25.933
AND THERE IS NO LONGER HEAT
THAT PUSHES IT OUT

01:10:25.933 --> 01:10:29.403
THE CORE COLLAPSES AND
AND THERE IS NO LONGER HEAT
IT CAN FORM A NEUTRON STAR...T

01:10:29.403 --> 01:10:32.440
THIS COLLAPSE CAN BE SO STRONG

01:10:32.440 --> 01:10:37.645
DEPENDING UPON THE ORIGINAL MASS
OF THE STAR, THAT IT OVERSHOOTS

01:10:38.079 --> 01:10:40.247
AND DOESN'T BECOME
A NEUTRON STAR

01:10:40.247 --> 01:10:45.019
BUT BECOME EVEN SMALLER, AND
THEN IT CAN BECOME A BLACK HOLE.

01:10:45.019 --> 01:10:48.055
IF YOU TAKE THE EARTH,
TO GIVE YOU AN EXAMPLE

01:10:48.055 --> 01:10:51.525
AND YOU TAKE A VISE, A BIG VISE,
AND YOU SQUEEZE THE EARTH--

01:10:51.525 --> 01:10:54.562
THE EARTH HAS A RADIUS
OF 6,400 KILOMETERS--

01:10:54.562 --> 01:10:56.731
IF YOU COULD MAKE THE RADIUS
THREE CENTIMETERS

01:10:57.164 --> 01:10:58.899
THE EARTH WOULD BECOME
A BLACK HOLE.

01:10:58.899 --> 01:11:00.201
THREE CENTIMETERS-- THIS BIG.

01:11:00.634 --> 01:11:03.671
THEN IT WOULD AUTOMATICALLY
FURTHER COLLAPSE ONTO ITSELF.

01:11:03.671 --> 01:11:06.273
NOTHING COULD STOP IT, AND
IT WOULD BECOME A BLACK HOLE.

01:11:06.273 --> 01:11:09.744
AND LIGHT COULD NEVER LEAVE IT.

01:11:09.744 --> 01:11:11.912
BECAUSE THEY ALL GO
AT THE SPEED OF LIGHT.

01:11:16.684 --> 01:11:20.154
Osgood:
FINDING SOMETHING THAT
DOESN'T GIVE OFF LIGHT--

01:11:20.154 --> 01:11:24.058
OR ANY OTHER KIND OF RADIATION--
IS TRICKY, TO SAY THE LEAST.

01:11:24.439 --> 01:11:26.227
IT'S NOT UNTIL THE EARLY '70s

01:11:26.227 --> 01:11:29.697
THAT ASTRONOMERS STUMBLE
ON THE FIRST INDIRECT EVIDENCE

01:11:29.697 --> 01:11:32.733
OF A BLACK HOLE.

01:11:32.733 --> 01:11:36.637
THE FIRST CLUE COMES
WHEN X-RAY TELESCOPES REVEAL

01:11:36.637 --> 01:11:39.673
AN AREA OF INTENSE
VIOLENCE AND TEMPERATURE

01:11:39.673 --> 01:11:41.842
IN THE CONSTELLATION CYGNUS.

01:11:41.842 --> 01:11:44.879
PAUL MURDIN IS ONE
OF MANY ASTRONOMERS

01:11:44.879 --> 01:11:47.047
WHO BEGIN TO FOCUS ON THIS AREA.

01:11:47.047 --> 01:11:51.385
WORKING WITH LOUISE WEBSTER,
HE FINDS A SUPERGIANT STAR

01:11:51.385 --> 01:11:53.988
ORBITING SOMETHING
THEY CAN'T SEE.

01:11:56.157 --> 01:11:59.627
LOGICALLY, THE SUPERGIANT
MUST BE CIRCLING

01:11:59.627 --> 01:12:02.229
A MUCH SMALLER AND DENSER STAR--

01:12:02.229 --> 01:12:06.567
ONE SO DENSE ITS GRAVITY IS
SUCKING HUGE AMOUNTS OF MATTER

01:12:06.567 --> 01:12:08.302
FROM ITS LARGER COMPANION.

01:12:08.736 --> 01:12:11.338
ONLY THIS COULD PRODUCE
THE INTENSE X RAYS

01:12:11.338 --> 01:12:13.507
OTHER ASTRONOMERS HAD DETECTED.

01:12:15.242 --> 01:12:17.411
FURTHER MEASUREMENTS REVEAL

01:12:17.411 --> 01:12:20.014
GRAVITY
FURTHEMUST BE GREATERREVEAL'S

01:12:20.014 --> 01:12:22.616
THAN ANYTHING DISCOVERED BEFORE.

01:12:22.616 --> 01:12:25.653
THE ONLY EXPLANATION
IS A BLACK HOLE.

01:12:29.557 --> 01:12:33.894
THERE IS STILL NO ABSOLUTE PROOF
THAT BLACK HOLES EXIST

01:12:33.894 --> 01:12:36.063
BUT FROM THE 1970s ON

01:12:36.063 --> 01:12:39.533
MOST SCIENTISTS HAVE COME
TO ACCEPT THEM AS REAL--

01:12:39.533 --> 01:12:41.702
INCREDIBLY STRANGE, BUT REAL.

01:12:41.702 --> 01:12:43.871
Lewin:
WHEREAS WITH A NEUTRON STAR

01:12:43.871 --> 01:12:46.473
AT LEAST YOU CAN IMAGINE
IT HAS A SURFACE

01:12:46.473 --> 01:12:48.642
AND YOU CAN LAND
ON THAT SURFACE.

01:12:48.642 --> 01:12:52.546
AND OKAY, IT IS A MIND-BOGGLING
MAGNETIC FIELD, ALL RIGHT

01:12:52.546 --> 01:12:54.281
BUT SO BE IT, IT'S THERE.

01:12:54.281 --> 01:12:56.884
AND OKAY, IT ROTATES
700 TIMES PER SECOND.

01:12:56.884 --> 01:12:59.486
BUT A BLACK HOLE HAS NO SURFACE

01:12:59.486 --> 01:13:03.824
SO YOU CAN'T EVEN TALK ABOUT
A SURFACE THAT ROTATES AROUND.

01:13:03.824 --> 01:13:08.596
IT DOESN'T EXIST, AND THERE IS
NOTIMETHAT YOU CAN DEFINE.

01:13:08.596 --> 01:13:10.764
THAT'S PRETTY BIZARRE.

01:13:10.764 --> 01:13:14.235
THAT GOES BEYOND,
TOTALLY BEYOND MY IMAGINATION

01:13:14.235 --> 01:13:16.403
I'LL BE VERY HONEST WITH YOU.

01:13:16.403 --> 01:13:19.006
BUT YET, IT'S ONE
OF MY SPECIALTIES.

01:13:19.006 --> 01:13:21.175
I MEASURE THEM, I FIND THEM.

01:13:21.175 --> 01:13:23.777
CAN I ENVISION THEM?

01:13:23.777 --> 01:13:25.512
NO.

01:13:29.850 --> 01:13:31.585
Osgood:
CURRENT THEORY HOLDS

01:13:31.585 --> 01:13:34.622
THAT THERE ARE BILLIONS OF
BLACK HOLES IN THE UNIVERSE

01:13:34.622 --> 01:13:38.092
INCLUDING ENORMOUS ONES AT
THE CENTER OF MOST GALAXIES.

01:13:42.863 --> 01:13:46.767
THESE ARE SO LARGE,
THEY MUST HAVE DEVOURED MILLIONS

01:13:46.767 --> 01:13:49.370
PERHAPS EVEN BILLIONS OF STARS.

01:13:52.840 --> 01:13:55.876
BUT EVEN THE BIRTH AND GROWTH
OF BLACK HOLES

01:13:55.876 --> 01:13:57.611
AREN'T NEARLY AS FANTASTIC

01:13:57.611 --> 01:14:00.648
AS THE CREATION OF
THE UNIVERSE ITSELF.

01:14:06.287 --> 01:14:08.022
Osgood:
FOR MOST OF HUMAN EXISTENCE

01:14:08.455 --> 01:14:10.624
THE QUESTION OF HOW
EVERYTHING BEGAN

01:14:10.624 --> 01:14:13.661
IS ONE THAT ONLY RELIGION
DARED TO ANSWER.

01:14:13.661 --> 01:14:15.829
BUT
DISCOVERY

01:14:15.829 --> 01:14:20.601
THAT THE UNIVERSE IS EXPANDING,
SOME SCIENTISTS BEGIN TO BELIEVE

01:14:20.601 --> 01:14:23.575
THAT THEY TOO MIGHT HAVE
SOMETHING TO OFFER.

01:14:23.575 --> 01:14:26.240
THEIR REASONING GOES
SOMETHING LIKE THIS:

01:14:26.240 --> 01:14:27.975
IF THE UNIVERSE IS EXPANDING

01:14:27.975 --> 01:14:30.577
THEN IN THE PAST,
IT MUST HAVE BEEN SMALLER.

01:14:30.577 --> 01:14:31.879
GO FAR ENOUGH BACK

01:14:32.313 --> 01:14:34.915
AND EVN
CRUNCHED TOGETHER

01:14:34.915 --> 01:14:37.084
IN A POINT OF INFINITE DENSITY.

01:14:37.084 --> 01:14:39.687
OUR UNIVERSE BEGAN, THEY SUGGEST

01:14:39.687 --> 01:14:41.422
WHEN THAT POINT EXPLODED

01:14:41.422 --> 01:14:44.892
CREATING THE EXPANSION
LL SEE TODAY.

01:14:44.892 --> 01:14:49.663
THIS VISION COMES TO BE CALLED
THE BIG BANG THEORY OF CREATION.

01:14:49.663 --> 01:14:53.567
AT THE START OF THE 1960s,
SCIENTISTS ARE EQUALLY DIVIDED

01:14:53.567 --> 01:14:55.302
BETWEEN THIS BIG BANG THEORY

01:14:55.302 --> 01:14:58.772
AND A COMPETING NOTION
THAT THE UNIVERSE IS ETERNAL

01:14:58.772 --> 01:15:00.507
CALLED THE STEADY-STATE THEORY.

01:15:00.507 --> 01:15:03.978
BUT THERE'S NO REAL HARD
EVIDENCE FOR EITHER ONE.

01:15:03.978 --> 01:15:06.146
IN FACT, ALMOST NO ONE EXPECTS

01:15:06.146 --> 01:15:08.315
THE DEBATE WILL EVER
BE RESOLVED.

01:15:11.785 --> 01:15:13.954
IN THE EARLY '60s, ROBERT DICKE

01:15:13.954 --> 01:15:16.557
AN ASTROPHYSICIST
AT PRINCETON UNIVERSITY

01:15:16.557 --> 01:15:19.159
COMES UP WITH WHAT HE THINKS
IS A WAY TO TEST

01:15:19.159 --> 01:15:22.629
WHETHER OR NOT THE UNIVERSE
STARTED WITH A BIG BANG.

01:15:22.629 --> 01:15:24.798
HE'S CONVINCED
THAT IF IT HAPPENED

01:15:24.798 --> 01:15:28.702
THE ENTIRE UNIVERSE SHOULD BE
FILLED WITH RADIATION

01:15:28.702 --> 01:15:30.871
LEFT FROM THE MOMENT
OF CREATION.

01:15:30.871 --> 01:15:34.775
Man:
BOB DICKE'S REASONING
WAS QUITE INTERESTING.

01:15:34.775 --> 01:15:38.679
HE REASONED THAT IF THE UNIVERSE
HAD GONE THROUGH

01:15:38.679 --> 01:15:40.414
THIS BIG BANG PHASE

01:15:40.414 --> 01:15:43.017
IT MUST HAVE BEEN VERY HOT
AND VERY DENSE

01:15:43.450 --> 01:15:46.487
AND THERE MUST HAVE A LOT OF
HEAT RADIATION

01:15:46.487 --> 01:15:47.788
VERY HIGH TEMPERATURE

01:15:47.788 --> 01:15:50.391
AND HE COULDN'T FIND
ANY THEORETICAL WAY

01:15:50.391 --> 01:15:52.559
TO GET RID OF THIS RADIATION.

01:15:52.559 --> 01:15:53.861
IT MUST STILL BE AROUND.

01:15:53.861 --> 01:15:56.897
IT MUST STILL BE AROUND.OOLE
D OFF BECAUSE
THE UNIVERSE EXPANDED

01:15:56.897 --> 01:16:00.367
BUT IT MUST STILL BE AROUND
AND IN THE MICROWAVE BAND

01:16:00.367 --> 01:16:02.102
THE BAND WHERE RADAR WORKS.

01:16:06.440 --> 01:16:09.476
Osgood:
IT'S A TRULY AMAZING
POSSIBILITY--

01:16:09.476 --> 01:16:11.211
15-BILLION-YEAR-OLD HEAT

01:16:11.211 --> 01:16:13.814
TRANSFORMED BY
THE EXPANSION OF SPACE

01:16:13.814 --> 01:16:15.549
INTO LOW-LEVEL RADIO STATIC

01:16:15.549 --> 01:16:18.585
THAT PERMEATES EVERY CORNER
OF THE UNIVERSE.

01:16:18.585 --> 01:16:21.622
IF IT'S THERE,
THE ONLY COSMOLOGICAL THEORY

01:16:21.622 --> 01:16:25.526
THAT CAN EXPLAIN HOW IT
GOT THERE IS THE BIG BANG.

01:16:27.694 --> 01:16:29.430
NICE THING ABOUT
DICKE'S THEORY IS...

01:16:29.430 --> 01:16:32.900
Osgood:
DICKE CONVINCES DAVID WILKINSON
AND ANOTHER YOUNG PHYSICIST

01:16:33.333 --> 01:16:34.635
TO BUILD AN ANTENNA

01:16:34.635 --> 01:16:37.237
AND SEARCH FOR THIS COSMIC
BACKGROUND RADIATION.

01:16:37.237 --> 01:16:40.274
...FIT ON A VERY SPECIFIC CURVE
CALLED THE BLACK BODY CURVE.

01:16:40.274 --> 01:16:42.876
Wilkinson:
WE WEREN'T IN ANY
PARTICULAR HURRY

01:16:43.255 --> 01:16:45.479
BECAUSE BOB DICKE'S IDEA
WAS SO ORIGINAL.

01:16:45.479 --> 01:16:47.214
WE WEREN'T TOO WORRIED

01:16:47.214 --> 01:16:50.250
ABOUT SOMEBODY ELSE
GETTING THERE BEFORE WE DID.

01:16:50.250 --> 01:16:52.853
SO WE CHARGED AHEAD
RATHER SLOWLY.

01:16:52.853 --> 01:16:55.889
WE HAD NO MICROWAVE EQUIPMENT
AT ALL.

01:16:55.889 --> 01:16:58.492
WE HAD TO ORDER THINGS NEW.

01:16:58.492 --> 01:17:01.962
WE WENT DOWN TO ARCH STREET
IN PHILADELPHIA

01:17:01.962 --> 01:17:05.866
AND DUG AROUND IN
THE WORLD WAR II SURPLUS SHOPS

01:17:05.866 --> 01:17:08.469
TO FIND THINGS THAT WERE CHEAP.

01:17:08.469 --> 01:17:12.372
BOB DICKE IS A RATHER
FRUGAL EXPERIMENTALIST

01:17:12.372 --> 01:17:16.710
SO IF WE COULD FIND IT IN
THE JUNK SHOP, WE DID THAT.

01:17:18.743 --> 01:17:21.915
Osgood:
THIS IS THE ANTENNA
THAT RESULTED.

01:17:21.915 --> 01:17:24.952
IT'S CAREFULLY CALIBRATED
USING SUPER-COLD HELIUM.

01:17:25.385 --> 01:17:27.121
WHILE WILKINSON IS BUILDING IT

01:17:27.121 --> 01:17:30.157
TWO OTHER SCIENTISTS,
JUST 30 MILES AWAY

01:17:30.157 --> 01:17:31.892
ARE SETTING UP AN EXPERIMENT

01:17:31.892 --> 01:17:35.362
THAT SEEMS TO HAVE NOTHING
TO DO WITH THE BIG BANG.

01:17:38.398 --> 01:17:40.567
WITH COLLEAGUE ARNO PENZIAS

01:17:40.567 --> 01:17:44.037
BOB WILSON PLANS TO USE
THIS MICROWAVE ANTENNA

01:17:44.037 --> 01:17:45.772
TO STUDY OUR GALAXY.

01:17:45.772 --> 01:17:47.941
UNAWARE OF DICKE'S IDEA.
TO STUDY OUR GALAXY. HE'S

01:17:47.941 --> 01:17:50.978
IN FACT, HE DOESN'T BELIEVE
IN THE BIG BANG

01:17:50.978 --> 01:17:55.315
BUT PREFERS A UNIVERSE
WITH NO BEGINNING OR END.

01:17:55.315 --> 01:17:57.050
Man:
I LIKED THE STEADY STATE.

01:17:57.050 --> 01:17:59.653
IT'S PHILOSOPHICALLY SATISFYING

01:18:00.087 --> 01:18:04.424
BECAUSE THERE'S NO END
TO THE UNIVERSE IN THE FUTURE.

01:18:04.424 --> 01:18:08.328
IT GOES ON FOREVER IN THE SAME
SORT OF STATE THAT IT IS.

01:18:08.328 --> 01:18:10.931
AND THERE'S NO BEGINNING
FOR IT, EITHER.

01:18:10.931 --> 01:18:13.534
SO PHYSICISTS GENERALLY
LIKE STEADY STATE

01:18:13.967 --> 01:18:17.004
BECAUSE THEY DON'T LIKE
TO HAVE TO HAVE A TIME

01:18:17.004 --> 01:18:19.606
BEYOND WHICH THEY
CAN'T KNOW ANYTHING.

01:18:21.341 --> 01:18:24.811
Osgood:
WILSON AND PENZIAS ARE THEN
JUST GETTING STARTED

01:18:24.811 --> 01:18:26.547
ON THEIR SCIENTIFIC CAREERS.

01:18:26.547 --> 01:18:28.715
THEY HAVE NO DESIRE
TO CONFRONT A PROBLEM

01:18:29.149 --> 01:18:32.186
AS DIFFICULT AS WHETHER OR NOT
THE UNIVERSE HAD A BEGINNING.

01:18:32.186 --> 01:18:36.957
THEY JUST WANT TO MAKE SOME
SMALL CONTRIBUTION TO ASTRONOMY.

01:18:39.560 --> 01:18:43.897
Wilson:
DOING SCIENCE BY OURSELVES
WAS A GREAT NEW ADVENTURE.

01:18:43.897 --> 01:18:46.500
WE SORT OF HAD A CHANCE
AT BELL LABS

01:18:46.500 --> 01:18:49.970
TO BECOME SCIENTISTS--
YOU KNOW, IN THE REAL SENSE--

01:18:49.970 --> 01:18:53.874
AND MAKE USE OF
THIS UNIQUE INSTRUMENT

01:18:53.874 --> 01:18:58.212
AND, YOU KNOW, WE REALLY
DEVOTED OURSELVES TO IT.

01:19:00.814 --> 01:19:03.417
Osgood:
WILSON AND PENZIAS BELIEVE

01:19:03.417 --> 01:19:06.887
THE HOLMDEL ANTENNA WILL MAKE
A GREAT RADIO TELESCOPE

01:19:06.887 --> 01:19:09.056
BECAUSE IT'S DESIGNED TO REJECT

01:19:09.056 --> 01:19:11.225
ALL EXTRANEOUS SIGNALS,
OR NOISE.

01:19:12.526 --> 01:19:15.895
VERY FIRST TIME
ALL EXTRANEOUS SIGNALS,
THEY USE ITUT FROM THE

01:19:15.895 --> 01:19:20.767
EXTRANEOUS NOISE IS EXACTLY
WHAT IT SEEMS TO BE PICKING UP.

01:19:21.201 --> 01:19:23.370
Wilson:
EVERY TIME WE STARTED UP

01:19:23.370 --> 01:19:25.105
WE SAW THE SAME NOISE LEVEL.

01:19:25.105 --> 01:19:27.274
EVERYWHERE IN THE SKY WE POINTED

01:19:27.274 --> 01:19:29.443
WE SAW THE SAME NOISE LEVEL.

01:19:29.443 --> 01:19:33.780
Osgood:
IT ISN'T A LOT OF NOISE,
BUT THEY FEAR IT'S ENOUGH

01:19:33.780 --> 01:19:36.383
TO COMPROMISE
SOME OF THEIR RESEARCH.

01:19:36.383 --> 01:19:39.419
SO THEY DECIDE TO FIND OUT
WHAT'S CAUSING IT

01:19:39.419 --> 01:19:41.154
AND GET RID OF IT.

01:19:43.323 --> 01:19:45.926
THEY CHECK TO SEE
IF IT'S THERE AT NIGHT.

01:19:45.926 --> 01:19:51.131
THEY CHECK TO SEE IF IT'S THERE
IN DIFFERENT SEASONS.

01:19:52.866 --> 01:19:55.035
THEY CHECK ALL POSSIBLE
GROUND-BASED SOURCES

01:19:55.035 --> 01:19:57.204
OF RADIO NOISE.

01:19:59.373 --> 01:20:02.409
THEY CHECK THE ANTENNA ITSELF
AND TAPE ALL ITS JOINTS.

01:20:04.578 --> 01:20:08.048
THEY DOUBLE-CHECK EVERY PIECE
OF EQUIPMENT IN THE SYSTEM.

01:20:08.048 --> 01:20:11.084
AND THE NOISE IS ALWAYS THERE.

01:20:15.856 --> 01:20:18.025
WITH FEW ALTERNATIVES
LEFT TO TRY

01:20:18.025 --> 01:20:20.983
THEY DECIDE TO CHECK
A REAL LONG SHOT.

01:20:24.965 --> 01:20:27.567
Wilson:
A SET OF PIGEONS
HAD STARTED ROOSTING

01:20:27.567 --> 01:20:31.038
UP IN THE THROAT OF THE THING,
AND OF COURSE THEY'D COATED IT

01:20:31.038 --> 01:20:33.206
WITH THE SAME WHITE
PIGEON DROPPINGS

01:20:33.206 --> 01:20:36.243
THAT YOU SEE ON STATUES
AND SO FORTH IN THE CITY.

01:20:36.243 --> 01:20:38.845
WE GOT A LADDER
FROM THE CARPENTERS

01:20:38.845 --> 01:20:42.749
AND A COUPLE OF PUSH BROOMS
AND SOME SCRUB BRUSHES

01:20:42.749 --> 01:20:44.918
AND SCRAPED OFF
THE DIFFICULT ONES

01:20:44.918 --> 01:20:47.954
AND SWEPT THE WHOLE THING OUT.

01:20:51.425 --> 01:20:53.160
Osgood:
THEY CHECK AGAIN

01:20:53.160 --> 01:20:56.630
AND REALIZE THEY COULD HAVE
LEFT THE PIGEONS ALONE.

01:20:56.630 --> 01:20:59.666
A YEAR OF THIS STRUGGLE
HAS LEFT THEM CONVINCED

01:20:59.666 --> 01:21:01.401
THE ANTENNA IS FINE.

01:21:01.401 --> 01:21:04.871
THE ONLY POSSIBILITY LEFT,
AND IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE

01:21:05.305 --> 01:21:08.342
IS THAT EVERY CORNER
OF THE UNIVERSE IS FILLED

01:21:08.342 --> 01:21:10.077
WITH THE SAME NOISE.

01:21:10.077 --> 01:21:14.414
DESPERATE, THEY BEGIN CALLING
OTHER ASTRONOMERS FOR HELP

01:21:14.414 --> 01:21:17.017
AND ONE SUGGESTS
CALLING BOB DICKE.

01:21:17.017 --> 01:21:20.053
AND THE PHONE RANG,
AND BOB PICKED IT UP

01:21:20.053 --> 01:21:23.523
AND IT WAS TWO GUYS FROM
BELL LABS WHO HAD A PROBLEM

01:21:23.523 --> 01:21:27.861
WHICH AT FIST DIDN'T SEEM
TO HAVE ANYTHING TO DO WITH US.

01:21:27.861 --> 01:21:30.030
WE DIDN'T LEARN VERY MUCH
ON THE TELEPHONE

01:21:30.464 --> 01:21:33.066
BUT THEY AGREED TO COME OUT
AND SEE WHAT WE HAD DONE

01:21:33.066 --> 01:21:35.235
AND TELL US ABOUT
WHAT THEY HAD IN MIND.

01:21:36.970 --> 01:21:38.271
UH, HE HUNG UP THE PHONE

01:21:38.271 --> 01:21:40.874
AND I'LL NEVER FORGET
EXACTLY WHAT HE SAID.

01:21:40.874 --> 01:21:42.175
THESE ARE HIS EXACT WORDS.

01:21:42.175 --> 01:21:44.778
HE SAID, "WELL, BOYS,
WE'VE BEEN SCOOPED."

01:21:46.513 --> 01:21:50.417
Osgood:
ROBERT WILSON AND ARNO PENZIAS
HAD ALREADY HEARD

01:21:50.417 --> 01:21:52.152
THE ECHO OF THE BIG BANG.

01:21:52.152 --> 01:21:55.188
THEIR ANNOYING BACKGROUND NOISE
WAS, IN FACT

01:21:55.188 --> 01:21:59.092
NOTHING LESS THAN A WHISPER
FROM CREATION ITSELF.

01:22:05.599 --> 01:22:09.069
IN THE BEGINNING,
SOME 15 BILLION YEARS AGO

01:22:09.503 --> 01:22:12.973
THE UNIVERSE EXPLODED
FROM A SINGLE POINT.

01:22:17.744 --> 01:22:24.684
LESS THAN ONE MINUTE LATER, IT'S
A MILLION BILLION MILES ACROSS.

01:22:24.684 --> 01:22:26.853
IT STILL HAS
AN AVERAGE TEMPERATURE

01:22:26.853 --> 01:22:28.588
OF A BILLION DEGREES.

01:22:37.264 --> 01:22:40.734
THE UNIVERSE CONTINUES
TO EXPAND AND COOL.

01:22:40.734 --> 01:22:43.770
GRADUALLY, GRAVITY
DRAWS TOGETHER ATOMS

01:22:43.770 --> 01:22:49.409
AND THEN CLUMPS OF ATOMS.

01:22:49.409 --> 01:22:51.578
AND GALAXIES ARE CREATED.

01:23:26.279 --> 01:23:30.617
EVENTUALLY, AROUND SOME
OF THE STARS, PLANETS FORM

01:23:30.617 --> 01:23:34.521
AND ON AT LEAST ONE,
LIFE BEGINS.

01:23:49.703 --> 01:23:54.040
IF EVERYTHING IN THE UNIVERSE
BEGAN IN A SINGLE POINT

01:23:54.040 --> 01:23:56.643
IT'S HARD NOT TO WONDER
WHAT IT TOOK

01:23:57.077 --> 01:24:00.981
TO GO FROM SUCH ULTIMATE
SIMPLICITY TO ALL OF THIS.

01:24:00.981 --> 01:24:04.451
MANY PHYSICISTS BELIEVE
THAT AT THE BEGINNING OF TIME

01:24:04.451 --> 01:24:08.788
THERE WAS ONLY A SINGLE PARTICLE
GOVERNED BY A SINGLE FORCE.

01:24:08.788 --> 01:24:12.692
FROM THAT STARTING POINT, WITHIN
A TINY FRACTION OF A SECOND

01:24:12.692 --> 01:24:15.729
PARTICLES LIKE PROTONS
AND ELECTRONS EVOLVED

01:24:16.162 --> 01:24:19.633
AND FORCES LIKE GRAVITY
AND MAGNETISM CAME INTO BEING

01:24:19.633 --> 01:24:22.669
BUT DID THE UNIVERSE
HAVE TO BE LIKE THIS?

01:24:22.669 --> 01:24:25.705
COULD IT HAVE TURNED OUT
ANY OTHER WAY?

01:24:25.705 --> 01:24:29.175
PERHAPS IF WE CAN WORK BACK
TO THE MOMENT OF CREATION

01:24:29.609 --> 01:24:31.778
TO THAT ULTIMATE PARTICLE
AND FORCE

01:24:31.778 --> 01:24:35.682
WE'LL COME TO UNDERSTAND WHY
THE UNIVERSE IS THE WAY IT IS

01:24:35.682 --> 01:24:37.417
AND EVEN TO EXPRESS IT

01:24:37.417 --> 01:24:40.453
IN WHAT PHYSICISTS CALL
"THE FINAL THEORY"

01:24:40.453 --> 01:24:44.791
WHICH, IT'S HOPED, CAN BE
CAPTURED IN A SINGLE EQUATION

01:24:45.225 --> 01:24:47.394
THAT CAN FIT ON A T-SHIRT.

01:24:47.394 --> 01:24:50.864
THIS MAY EXPLAIN EVERYTHING.

01:24:58.238 --> 01:25:01.274
WHEN WE LOOK AT NATURE,
WE SEE THE COMPLEXITIES

01:25:01.274 --> 01:25:03.443
THE DIFFERENCES AMONG THINGS.

01:25:04.744 --> 01:25:07.781
BUT SCIENTISTS TEND
TO LOOK FOR THE CONNECTIONS

01:25:07.781 --> 01:25:10.817
THE SIMPLICITY THAT LIES
AT THE HEART OF IT ALL.

01:25:14.287 --> 01:25:17.757
Man:
THE MORE YOU LEARN ABOUT NATURE,
THE SIMPLER IT LOOKS.

01:25:17.757 --> 01:25:20.360
AND THAT'S WHY I THINK
WE WILL FIND A FINAL THEORY

01:25:20.360 --> 01:25:22.963
BECAUSE ALTHOUGH I CAN IMAGINE
THINGS GETTING

01:25:22.963 --> 01:25:25.999
INFINITELY MORE COMPLICATED,
COMPLICATION WITHOUT END

01:25:25.999 --> 01:25:28.055
I CAN'T IMAGINE
SIMPLICITY WITHOUT END.

01:25:28.055 --> 01:25:30.770
THE WHOLE PROGRESS
OF PHYSICS HAS BEEN

01:25:30.770 --> 01:25:34.240
TOE
DESCRIPTION OF NATURE

01:25:34.240 --> 01:25:36.409
AND HOW SIMPLE CAN THINGS GET?

01:25:36.409 --> 01:25:38.578
SIMPLICITY MUST
FINALLY TERMINATE.

01:25:38.578 --> 01:25:40.747
THERE MUST BE
SOMETHING SO SIMPLE

01:25:40.747 --> 01:25:46.820
THAT WE CAN'T IMAGINE
ANYTHING MORE SIMPLE.

01:25:46.820 --> 01:25:49.815
Osgood:
BUT IN THE YEARS
FOLLOWING WORLD WAR II

01:25:49.815 --> 01:25:51.157
PHYSICISTS ARE STUNNED

01:25:51.591 --> 01:25:55.495
TO FIND THEIR DREAM OF ULTIMATE
SIMPLICITY SLIPPING AWAY.

01:25:55.495 --> 01:25:58.098
EXPERIMENTS MEANT
TO REVEAL SIMPLICITY

01:25:58.098 --> 01:25:59.833
FIND EVER GREATER COMPLEXITY.

01:26:05.038 --> 01:26:08.074
Newsreel announcer:
BERKELEY CALIFORNIA,
HOME OF THE BEVATRON.

01:26:08.508 --> 01:26:10.677
THE B.E.V. STANDS FOR
BILLIONS OF ELECTRON VOLTS...

01:26:10.677 --> 01:26:13.279
WORLD'S MOST POWERFUL
ATOM SMASHER.

01:26:15.015 --> 01:26:18.051
Osgood:
IT'S THE BEGINNING
OF THE ERA OF BIG SCIENCE.

01:26:19.352 --> 01:26:21.521
GIANT ATOM SMASHERS ARE BUILT

01:26:21.521 --> 01:26:24.991
TO ACCELERATE SUBATOMIC
PARTICLES TOS

01:26:25.425 --> 01:26:27.594
AND SMASH THEM INTO OTHER ATOMS.

01:26:27.594 --> 01:26:31.498
Galison:
EACH NEW ACCELERATOR BUILT
AFTER THE WAR WAS MORE POWERFUL

01:26:31.498 --> 01:26:33.667
THAN THE ONE THAT CAME BEFORE.

01:26:33.667 --> 01:26:36.703
EACH WAS ABLE TO RAM PARTICLES
INTO EACH OTHER HARDER

01:26:36.703 --> 01:26:40.607
AND TO SHOW WHAT WAS HAPPENING
AT A SMALLER AND SMALLER SCALE.

01:26:40.607 --> 01:26:42.776
IT WAS JUST
LIKE THE TELESCOPES.

01:26:42.776 --> 01:26:44.944
WITH EACH NEW TELESCOPE
THAT WAS BUILT

01:26:44.944 --> 01:26:48.415
YOU COULD SEE FURTHER OUT
INTO SPACE, GATHER MORE LIGHT

01:26:48.415 --> 01:26:50.583
RESOLVE OBJECTS MORE PRECISELY.

01:26:50.583 --> 01:26:52.318
WITH EACH NEW ACCELERATOR

01:26:52.318 --> 01:26:54.921
PEOPLE WERE ABLE TO SEE
DEEPER INTO MATTER

01:26:54.921 --> 01:26:59.693
MORE PRECISELY, BETTER
RESOLUTION, SMALLER SCALE.

01:26:59.693 --> 01:27:01.861
Osgood:
PHOTOGRAPHS OF THE TRACKS

01:27:01.861 --> 01:27:04.898
OF THE OBJECTS PRODUCED
IN THESE ACCELERATORS

01:27:04.898 --> 01:27:07.067
REVEAL A MULTITUDE
OF NEW PARTICLES

01:27:07.067 --> 01:27:09.235
THAT SEEM JUST AS FUNDAMENTAL

01:27:09.235 --> 01:27:12.272
AS THE FAMILIAR PROTCTRON.

01:27:12.272 --> 01:27:16.176
Kaku:
WE WERE LITERALLY DROWNING
IN SUBATOMIC PARTICLES.

01:27:16.176 --> 01:27:18.778
ONE YEAR,
OUT OF SHEER FRUSTRATION

01:27:18.778 --> 01:27:23.116
J. ROBERT OPPENHEIMER, FATHER
OF THE ATOMIC BOMB, STATED

01:27:23.116 --> 01:27:24.417
THAT THE PHYSICIST

01:27:24.417 --> 01:27:27.887
WHO DOES NOT DISCOVER
A NEW PARTICLE THAT YEAR

01:27:27.887 --> 01:27:30.924
SHOULD WIN
THE NOBEL PRIZE IN PHYSICS.

01:27:30.924 --> 01:27:33.960
THERE WERE HUNDREDS
AND HUNDREDS OF PARTICLES

01:27:33.960 --> 01:27:37.430
WHICH LOOKED JUST AS
ELEMENTARY AS THE PROTON.

01:27:37.430 --> 01:27:40.900
IT BECAME CLEAR THAT
IF ELEMENTARY MEANT ANYTHING

01:27:40.900 --> 01:27:43.937
EITHER THERE WAS SOMETHING
MORE ELEMENTARY

01:27:45.672 --> 01:27:47.841
OR PERHAPS THEY WERE
ALL ELEMENTARY--??

01:27:48.274 --> 01:27:49.142
A FRIGHTENING IDEA.

01:27:50.877 --> 01:27:54.347
Osgood:
AMONG THE PHYSICISTS UNHAPPY
WITH ALL THIS COMPLICATION

01:27:54.347 --> 01:27:57.383
IS A BRASH YOUNG THEORIST
NAMED MURRAY GELL-MANN.

01:27:59.552 --> 01:28:00.854
BY THE AGE OF 25

01:28:01.287 --> 01:28:04.758
GELL-MANN IS ALREADY WELL KNOWN
IN THE WORLD OF PHYSICS

01:28:05.191 --> 01:28:08.228
FOR HIS ENCYCLOPEDIC INTERESTS
AND KNOWLEDGE

01:28:08.228 --> 01:28:09.963
HIS QUICK AND CREATIVE MIND

01:28:09.963 --> 01:28:12.999
AND HIS FREQUENTLY ABRASIVE
PERSONAL STYLE.

01:28:14.615 --> 01:28:16.469
A COLLEAGUE SAYS OF HIM

01:28:16.469 --> 01:28:20.373
AY HAS NO
PARTICULAR TALENT FOR PHYSICSRR

01:28:20.373 --> 01:28:24.711
BUT HE'S SO SMART,
HE'S A GREAT PHYSICIST ANYWAY."

01:28:24.711 --> 01:28:27.747
THE IMPORTANT THING IS FIRST TO
STEEP YOURSELF IN THE PROBM

01:28:27.747 --> 01:28:30.784
TO LOOK AT THE PUZZLE,
ALL THE PIECES OF THE PUZZLE.

01:28:30.784 --> 01:28:33.820
Osgood:
BY LOOKING FOR PATTERNS
AND SYMMETRIES

01:28:33.820 --> 01:28:35.121
GELL-MANN FINDS A WAY

01:28:35.121 --> 01:28:37.724
TO ORGANIZE ALL THE NEWLY
DISCOVERED PARTICLES

01:28:37.724 --> 01:28:39.025
INTO FAMILIES.

01:28:40.760 --> 01:28:43.363
THEN, INSPIRED
BY A CHANCE ENCOUNTER

01:28:43.363 --> 01:28:46.833
DURING A VISIT TO COLUMBIA
UNIVERSITY IN NEW YORK

01:28:46.833 --> 01:28:49.435
HE TAKES A GIANT STEP
TOWARD SIMPLICITY.

01:28:51.604 --> 01:28:55.074
Kaku:
OVER LUNCH, A PHYSICIST
APPROACHED HIM AND SAID

01:28:55.074 --> 01:28:58.978
"ISN'T IT POSSIBLE THAT YOUR
THEORIES COULD BE EXPLAINED

01:28:58.978 --> 01:29:02.882
BY POSTULATING THREE EVEN
MORE FUNDAMENTAL PARTICLES?"

01:29:02.882 --> 01:29:06.786
WELL, EYONE AT THAT TABLE
DISMISSED THAT IDEA IMMEDIATELY

01:29:06.786 --> 01:29:11.124
AND THEY P TO
THIS PHYSICIST WHAT WAS WRONG.

01:29:11.124 --> 01:29:14.160
YOU WOULD HAVE FRACTIONALLY
CHARGED PARTICLES

01:29:14.160 --> 01:29:16.329
AN OUTRAGEOUS, RIDICULOUS IDEA

01:29:16.763 --> 01:29:18.064
BECAUSE EVERYONE KNEW

01:29:18.064 --> 01:29:22.402
THAT PARTICLES WERE EITHER
PLUS ONE OR MINUS ONE IN CHARGE

01:29:22.402 --> 01:29:24.571
NEVER ONE-THIRD OR TWO-THIRDS.

01:29:26.306 --> 01:29:28.908
Osgood:
BUT OVER THE MONTHS THAT FOLLOW

01:29:28.908 --> 01:29:33.246
GELL-MANN GROWS TO LOVE THE IDEA
OF THIS DEEPER LEVEL OF REALITY.

01:29:33.246 --> 01:29:36.282
THE FACT NO ONE'S EVER SEEN
PARTICLES THIS BIZARRE

01:29:36.282 --> 01:29:38.451
HE DECIDES ISN'T HIS PROBLEM.

01:29:41.921 --> 01:29:50.163
IN EARLY 1964, GELL-MANN
PROPOSES TO THE WORLD

01:29:50.163 --> 01:29:51.898
HE CALLS "QUARKS."

01:29:51.898 --> 01:29:55.368
HIS THREE QUARKS COULD COMBINE
IN DIFFERENT WAYS

01:30:00.139 --> 01:30:02.742
IT WOULD SIMPLIFY,
ORGANIZE

01:30:02.742 --> 01:30:05.345
IT WAS A GREAT
SCIENTIFIC ADVANCE.

01:30:05.345 --> 01:30:08.381
THE PROBLEM WAS THAT NO ONE
HAD EVER SEEN ANYTHING

01:30:08.381 --> 01:30:10.116
THAT LOOKED LIKE A QUARK.

01:30:11.417 --> 01:30:13.152
NOW, WHAT ARE THE QUARKS?

01:30:13.152 --> 01:30:15.321
ARE THEY ACTUALLY REAL OBJECTS?

01:30:15.321 --> 01:30:19.225
WELTAL FRIENDS
ARE MAKING A SEARCH FOR THEM

01:30:19.225 --> 01:30:20.960
IN ALL SORTS OF PLACES.

01:30:20.960 --> 01:30:24.430
ONE ATOMIC SPECTROSCOPIST
FRIEND OF MINE CALLS ME UP

01:30:24.430 --> 01:30:27.901
SOMETIMES AT MIDNIGHT HIS P
ROGRESS

01:30:27.901 --> 01:30:30.503
IN A SEARCH FOR QUARKS
IN SEAWATER.

01:30:30.503 --> 01:30:33.973
MOST THINGS WITH CURIOUS
CHEMICAL BEHAVIOR IN THE OCEAN

01:30:33.973 --> 01:30:35.708
END UP EATEN BY OYSTERS.

01:30:35.708 --> 01:30:37.877
(laughter)

01:30:37.877 --> 01:30:40.046
AND SO NOW
HE'S GRINDING UP OYSTERS...

01:30:40.046 --> 01:30:41.347
(laughter)

01:30:41.347 --> 01:30:44.384
AND LOOKING FOR THE ATOMIC
LEVELS IN THE OYSTERS.

01:30:44.817 --> 01:30:46.986
SO FAR, THOUGH, NO QUARKS.

01:30:46.986 --> 01:30:50.023
Kaku:
PHYSICISTS WERE FACED
WITH A PARADOX:

01:30:50.456 --> 01:30:51.758
WHERE WERE THE QUARKS?

01:30:51.758 --> 01:30:53.493
EVERYWHERE WE LOOKED

01:30:53.493 --> 01:30:57.397
WE COULD NOT FIND ANY PHYSICAL
EVIDENCE FOR THE QUARKS

01:30:57.397 --> 01:30:59.999
AND IN FACT,
SOME PHYSICISTS EVEN BEGAN

01:30:59.999 --> 01:31:03.036
TO DOUBT THE CORRECTNESS
OF THE THEORY.

01:31:03.036 --> 01:31:04.337
HOWEVER, OVER THE YEARS

01:31:04.771 --> 01:31:06.940
INDIRECT EVIDENCE BEGAN
TO TRICKLE IN

01:31:06.940 --> 01:31:08.675
CONFIRMING THIS THEORY.

01:31:08.675 --> 01:31:13.012
AND NOW WHEN EXPERIMENTERS
TAKE A HARD LOOK AT THE PROTON

01:31:13.012 --> 01:31:21.254
THEY SEE STRONG EVIDENCE
OF THE QUARKS INSIDE.

01:31:21.254 --> 01:31:22.989
FOR STARTERS, THEY'RE SO SMALL

01:31:22.989 --> 01:31:26.893
IT'S HARD TO APPLY TO THEM
OUR NORMAL NOTIONS OF SIZE.

01:31:26.893 --> 01:31:29.495
HEM
AS POINTS. E T

01:31:30.797 --> 01:31:31.664
POINTS? COME ON!

01:31:31.664 --> 01:31:32.966
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, POINTS?

01:31:32.966 --> 01:31:35.568
HOW CAN SOMETHING HAVE
A MASS AND A CHARGE

01:31:35.568 --> 01:31:36.869
AND BE A POINT?

01:31:36.869 --> 01:31:39.038
WELL, IT TAKES A LITTLE...

01:31:39.038 --> 01:31:42.508
A FEW MUSCLES IN THE MIND
THAT HAVN

01:31:42.508 --> 01:31:44.677
BUT IF YOU WORK ON THEM
FOR A WHILE

01:31:44.677 --> 01:31:46.846
YOU CAN IMAGINE SUCH AN OBJECT.

01:31:46.846 --> 01:31:49.882
IT'S A LITTLE BIT
LIKE ALICE IN WONDERLAND.

01:31:49.882 --> 01:31:53.786
REMEMBER THE CHESHIRE CAT
SITTING ON THE TREE, SMILING

01:31:53.786 --> 01:31:58.124
AND ALICE IS NOTICING

01:31:58.124 --> 01:32:00.727
WHEN THE CAT DISAPPEARS,
THE SMILE IS LEFT BEHIND?

01:32:00.727 --> 01:32:02.462
YOU REMEMBER THAT?

01:32:02.462 --> 01:32:05.932
WELL, IN A WAY YOU CAN LOOK
AT THAT AS YOU TAKE A QUARK

01:32:05.932 --> 01:32:07.667
AND IT'S SPINNING,
AND IT HAS A...

01:32:07.667 --> 01:32:09.402
IT'S SPHERICAL, IF YOU LIKE

01:32:09.402 --> 01:32:11.571
AND IT HAS MASS
AND CHARGE AND SPIN

01:32:11.571 --> 01:32:15.041
AND ALL THESE OTHER PROPERTIES
THAT WE LIKE TO MEASURE ABOUT IT

01:32:15.041 --> 01:32:17.643
BUT IN FRONT OF YOUR EYES,
IT'S SHRINKING

01:32:17.643 --> 01:32:19.812
AND FINALLY, IT... POOF!
SHRINKS TO A POINT

01:32:19.812 --> 01:32:22.415
LEAVING BEHIND ITS SPIN,
ITS CHARGE, ITS MASS

01:32:22.415 --> 01:32:25.451
AND IF IT HAS A SMILE,
LEAVING BEHIND ITS SMILE.

01:32:25.451 --> 01:32:27.620
THAT'S THE IDEA
OF POINT PARTICLES.

01:32:32.392 --> 01:32:35.862
Osgood:
WITH QUARKS, PHYSICS' JOURNEY
INTO THE HEART OF MATTER

01:32:35.862 --> 01:32:38.031
TAKES A GIANT STEP
TOWARD ITS GOAL

01:32:38.031 --> 01:32:41.934
OF FINDING AN ULTIMATE PARTICLE
FROM WHICH EVERYTHING IS MADE.

01:32:41.934 --> 01:32:45.838
INSTEAD OF HUNDREDS OF
FUNDAMENTAL PARTICLES IN NATURE

01:32:45.838 --> 01:32:48.875
NOW THERE ARE SIMPLY THREE:
ELECTRONS, QUARKS

01:32:48.875 --> 01:32:52.345
AND NEUTRINOS, TINY PARTICLES
WITH ALMOST NO MASS

01:32:52.345 --> 01:32:55.381
THAT RARELY INTERACT
WITH THE STUFF WE'RE MADE OF.

01:33:02.755 --> 01:33:05.792
THE SEARCH FOR A SINGLE
FUNDAMENTAL PARTICLE

01:33:05.792 --> 01:33:08.828
IS MATCHED BYR A SINGLE FORC
E

01:33:08.828 --> 01:33:11.864
THAT GOVERNS THE BEHAVIOR
OF EVERYTHING.

01:33:14.033 --> 01:33:16.202
THIS WAS ALBERT EINSTEIN'S
GREAT QUEST

01:33:16.636 --> 01:33:18.805
FOR THE LAST 25 YEARS
OF HIS LIFE.

01:33:18.805 --> 01:33:21.841
MORE THAN ONCE,
HE THOUGHT HE HAD DONE IT

01:33:21.841 --> 01:33:24.877
ONLY TO LEARN HIS SOLUTION
WAS FATALLY FLAWED.

01:33:28.347 --> 01:33:31.818
WHEN EINSTEIN WAS WORKING
ON UNIFICATION

01:33:31.818 --> 01:33:36.155
HE RECOGNIZED TWO FORCES:
GRAVITY AND ELECTROMAGNETISM.

01:33:36.155 --> 01:33:40.927
BUT TODAY, PHYSICISTS HAVE
TO DEAL WITH TWO OTHERS:

01:33:40.927 --> 01:33:43.963
THE STRONG FORCE
AND THE WEAK FORCE.

01:33:43.963 --> 01:33:47.867
THE WEAK FORCE IS RESPONSIBLE
FOR MANY FORMS OF RADIOACTIVITY.

01:33:47.867 --> 01:33:50.903
THE STRONG FORCE HOLDS
OUR NUCLEUS TOGETHER.

01:33:50.903 --> 01:33:54.807
THE NUCLEUS IS FULL OF PROTONS,
WHICH ALL HAVE POSITIVE CHARGES.

01:33:55.241 --> 01:33:58.277
THE NUCLEUS IS FULL OF PROTONS,
WHICH ALL HAVE POSITIVE CHARGES.
AND IF THERE WAS NOTHING
TO HOLD THEM TOGETHER

01:33:58.277 --> 01:34:01.314
THE ELECTRIC FORCES
WOULD MAKE THEM FLY APART

01:34:01.314 --> 01:34:03.483
BECAUSE EQUAL CHARGES
ARE REPELLED.

01:34:03.483 --> 01:34:06.953
THE STRONG FORCE
PREVENTS THAT FROM HAPPENING.

01:34:09.555 --> 01:34:12.592
Osgood:
ONE OF THE PHYSICISTS
WHO PLAYS A KEY ROLE

01:34:12.592 --> 01:34:15.628
IN THE QUEST FOR UNIFICATION
IS STEPHEN WEINBERG.

01:34:15.628 --> 01:34:20.399
HIS SPECIALTY IS THE TWO FORCES
WITHIN THE ATOMIC NUCLEUS:

01:34:20.399 --> 01:34:23.002
THE WEAK AND THE STRONG.

01:34:23.002 --> 01:34:26.906
Weberg:
LIKE A LOT OF OTHER PHYSICISTS,
I GOT STARTED WITH CHEMISTRY.

01:34:26.906 --> 01:34:29.431
I HAD A HAND-ME-DOWN
CHEMISTRY SET

01:34:29.431 --> 01:34:32.545
THAT WAS GIVEN TO ME
BY AN OLDER COUSIN.

01:34:32.545 --> 01:34:36.015
FIRST I JUST LIKED TO PLAY WITH
THE POWDERS AND THE LIQUIDS

01:34:36.015 --> 01:34:38.618
AND MAKE COLORED SMOKE
AND THINGS LIKE THAT

01:34:38.618 --> 01:34:40.353
AND GRADUALLY,
JUST READING ABOUT IT

01:34:40.786 --> 01:34:41.654
I BECAME AWARE

01:34:42.088 --> 01:34:44.690
THAT WHAT WENT ON INSIDE AN ATOM
WAS SOMETHING

01:34:44.690 --> 01:34:48.161
THAT COULDN'T BE EXPLAINED
IN TERMS OF ORDINARY THINGS

01:34:48.161 --> 01:34:52.064
THAT I KNEW ABOUT
IN EVERYDAY LIFE.

01:34:52.064 --> 01:34:55.101
THERE WAS SOMETHING
STRANGE AND WONDERFUL

01:34:55.101 --> 01:34:57.703
ABOUT PHYSICS,
WHICH WAS THE SCIENCE

01:34:57.703 --> 01:35:00.306
THAT GOVERNED WHAT GOES ON
IMS.

01:35:00.740 --> 01:35:06.812
Osgood:
THAT FEELING ABOUT PHYSICS
STAYS WITH WEINBERG

01:35:08.981 --> 01:35:12.018
IN THE LATE '60s,
HE'S STRUGGLING UNSUCCESSFULLY

01:35:12.018 --> 01:35:14.187
TO USE CERTAIN
MATHEMATICAL IDEAS

01:35:14.187 --> 01:35:16.355
TO MAKE SENSE
OF THE STRONG FORCE

01:35:16.355 --> 01:35:19.392
THE ONE THAT HOLDS
ATOMIC NUCLEI TOGETHER.

01:35:20.693 --> 01:35:22.862
Weinberg:
AND THEN AT A CERTAIN POINT

01:35:22.862 --> 01:35:25.464
I THINK WHEN I WAS DRIVING
MY CAR TO M.I.T.

01:35:25.464 --> 01:35:28.501
I REALIZED, MY GOODNESS,
THIS KIND OF MATHEMATICAL IDEA

01:35:28.501 --> 01:35:30.670
ALTHOUGH IT'S A COMPLETE LOSER

01:35:30.670 --> 01:35:33.272
AS FAR AS THE STRONG FORCES
ARE CONCERNED

01:35:33.272 --> 01:35:36.309
IS JUST WHAT WE NEED TO MAKE
A THEORY OF THE WEAK FORCE.

01:35:36.309 --> 01:35:39.779
AND TO MY SURPRISE, ALTHOUGH
CERTAINLY NOT MY DISAPPOINTMENT

01:35:39.779 --> 01:35:41.514
WHAT CAME OUT AT THE END

01:35:41.514 --> 01:35:43.683
WAS NOT JUST THE THEORY
OF THE WEAK FORCES

01:35:43.683 --> 01:35:46.285
BUT, INEVITABLY,
A UNIFIED THEORY

01:35:46.285 --> 01:35:48.888
OF WEAK AND
ELECTROMAGNETIC FORCES.

01:35:48.888 --> 01:35:52.358
ALL OF A SUDDEN,
FROM FOUR FUNDAMENTAL FORCES

01:35:52.358 --> 01:35:54.527
WE NOW HAD THREE
FUNDAMENTAL FORCES

01:35:54.527 --> 01:35:58.864
AND THIS CHANGED THE ENTIRE
TERRAIN OF THEORETICAL PHYSICS.

01:35:58.864 --> 01:36:01.901
Osgood:
IN ORDER TO TEST
WEINBERG'S THEORY

01:36:02.335 --> 01:36:06.239
THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITY SPENDS
A STAGGERING $150 MILLION

01:36:06.239 --> 01:36:08.407
TO MODIFY AND MAKE MORE POWERFUL

01:36:08.407 --> 01:36:11.010
ITS LARGEST PARTICLE
ACCELERATOR.

01:36:12.311 --> 01:36:16.215
THE PROT??S ARE IN THE MACHINE.

01:36:16.215 --> 01:36:19.252
WE'RE NOW IN THE COUNTDOWN.

01:36:27.927 --> 01:36:32.265
Osgood:
IN THE SUBATOMIC SHRAPNEL
CREATED IN THESE COLLISIONS

01:36:32.265 --> 01:36:34.433
LIES THE EVIDENCE THAT CONFIRMS

01:36:34.433 --> 01:36:37.470
THE CORRECTNESS
OF ELECTRO-WEAK UNIFICATION.

01:36:37.470 --> 01:36:41.374
THE FOUR FUNDAMENTAL FORCES
ARE NOW THREE.

01:36:41.374 --> 01:36:45.655
BUT JUST AS THREE TYPES
OF PARTICLES DOESN'T SATISFY

01:36:45.655 --> 01:36:48.314
NEITHER DOES THREE FORCES.

01:36:51.350 --> 01:36:53.085
IN THE MID-1980s

01:36:53.085 --> 01:36:55.254
WORK BEGINS ON WHAT
MOST PHYSICISTS BELIEVE

01:36:55.254 --> 01:36:58.724
IS THE KEY TO GETTING EVEN
CLOSER TO THE HEART OF MATTER.

01:37:00.459 --> 01:37:05.665
IT'S CALLED THE SUPERCONDUCTING
SUPERCOLLIDER, OR S.S.C.

01:37:07.833 --> 01:37:10.870
WITH AN UNDERGROUND
PARTICLE RING 50 MILES LONG

01:37:10.870 --> 01:37:14.774
IT'S DESIGNED TO RE-CREATE
THE CONDITIONS OF THE UNIVERSE

01:37:14.774 --> 01:37:18.678
IN ITS FIRST
TRILLION-TRILLION-TRILLIONTH
OF A SECOND.

01:37:20.846 --> 01:37:22.581
IT WAS TO BE A DEVICE SO LARGE

01:37:22.581 --> 01:37:24.750
IT WOULD ENCLOSE TOWNS
INSIDE IT.

01:37:24.750 --> 01:37:26.919
IT WAS A MACHINE
THAT WOULD REQUIRE BUSES

01:37:26.919 --> 01:37:29.088
TO GET FROM ONE PART TO ANOTHER.

01:37:29.088 --> 01:37:32.124
IT WAS A MACHINE THAT
WOULD SHIP VOLUMES OF DATA

01:37:32.124 --> 01:37:34.727
EQUIVALENT TO THE ENTIRE
LIBRARY OF CONGRESS

01:37:34.727 --> 01:37:37.330
OUT TO DISTANT LABORATORIES
AROUND THE WORLD

01:37:37.330 --> 01:37:39.065
WITH AMAZING FREQUENCY.

01:37:39.065 --> 01:37:40.800
THE DETECTORS, THE SITES

01:37:40.800 --> 01:37:43.402
WHERE THE ACTUAL PHYSICS
WOULD BE CONDUCTED

01:37:43.402 --> 01:37:45.137
WOULD COST
A BILLION DOLLARS APIECE

01:37:45.137 --> 01:37:47.740
AND HAVE SOMEWHERE NEAR
A THOUSAND PHYSICISTS

01:37:47.740 --> 01:37:50.343
AND PROBABLY AN EQUIVALENT
NUMBER OF TECHNICIANS

01:37:50.343 --> 01:37:52.078
AT EACH ONE.

01:37:53.813 --> 01:37:57.717
Osgood:
BUT IN 1993, AFTER
AN INVESTMENT OF $2 BILLION

01:37:57.717 --> 01:38:01.620
CONSTRUCTION ON THE S.S.C.
IS HALTED.

01:38:03.789 --> 01:38:07.693
YEARS OF ESCALATING COSTS HAVE
ERODED CONGRESSIONAL SUPPORT.

01:38:07.693 --> 01:38:12.031
THE MESSAGE TO SCIENTISTS IS,
FIND ANOTHER WAY TO HUNT

01:38:12.031 --> 01:38:16.369
FOR THE ULTIMATE PARTICLE
AND THE ULTIMATE FORCE.

01:38:16.369 --> 01:38:18.971
PHYSICISTS ARE DEVASTATED.

01:38:21.047 --> 01:38:23.743
Galison:
WHEN THE AMERICAN PARTICLE
PHYSICS COMMUNITY

01:38:23.743 --> 01:38:25.478
GAMBLED ON THE S.S.C.

01:38:25.478 --> 01:38:28.948
THEY HAD ESSENTIALLY TO SHUT
DOWN PROGRAM AFTER PROGRAM

01:38:28.948 --> 01:38:32.418
IN THE HOPES THAT THEY COULD
CONVINCE THE POLITICIANS

01:38:32.418 --> 01:38:34.153
THAT BY MAKING THESE SACRIFICES

01:38:34.153 --> 01:38:36.756
THEY SHOULD RECEIVE
THE AMOUNT OF FUNDS

01:38:36.756 --> 01:38:40.226
NECESSARY TO BUILD THE
SUPERCONDUCTING SUPERCOLLIDER.

01:38:40.226 --> 01:38:41.961
WHEN THE S.S.C. WAS CANCELED

01:38:41.961 --> 01:38:44.563
THEY ESSENTIALLY
LOST EVERYTHING.

01:38:44.563 --> 01:38:48.033
(playing Bach sonata)

01:38:53.239 --> 01:38:57.143
Osgood:
EVEN STILL, THE SEARCH
FOR UNIFICATION GOES ON.

01:38:57.143 --> 01:38:59.311
IN THE 1980s,
THEORISTS PROPOSE

01:38:59.311 --> 01:39:01.480
THAT AT THE HEART OF EVERYTHING

01:39:01.480 --> 01:39:04.517
ARE INFINITESIMALLY
SMALL VIBRATING STRINGS.

01:39:04.517 --> 01:39:06.685
STRING THEORY, QUITE SIMPLY

01:39:06.685 --> 01:39:09.288
IS THE MOST EXCITING IDEA
TO HIT PHYSICS

01:39:09.288 --> 01:39:11.891
SINCE THE DAYS
OF EINSTEIN AND BOHR.

01:39:11.891 --> 01:39:14.493
IT MAY WELL BE
THE FINAL THEORY--

01:39:14.493 --> 01:39:17.530
THE ONE THAT EXPLAINS
ABSOLUTELY EVERYTHING.

01:39:21.434 --> 01:39:23.169
Kaku:
THE PYTHAGOREANS BELIEVED

01:39:23.169 --> 01:39:25.337
THAT MUSIC WAS THE LANGUAGE
OF NATURE;

01:39:25.337 --> 01:39:27.506
THAT THE HARMONIES
ON A VIOLIN STRING--

01:39:27.506 --> 01:39:30.109
WHICH THEY WORKED OUT
FOR THE FIRST TIME IN HISTORY--

01:39:30.109 --> 01:39:31.844
WERE THE HARMONIES
OF THE UNIVERSE.

01:39:31.844 --> 01:39:35.314
AND THEY THOUGHT THAT ALL AROUND
US, SURROUNDING US WAS MUSIC--

01:39:35.314 --> 01:39:36.615
THE MUSIC OF THE SPHERES.

01:39:36.615 --> 01:39:39.218
UNFORTUNATELY, THAT IDEA
NEVER GOT ANYWHERE

01:39:39.218 --> 01:39:41.821
BECAUSE THAT COULDN'T
EXPLAIN THE ELEMENTS.

01:39:41.821 --> 01:39:45.291
NOW WE THINK THAT IF I HAVE
A SUPER-POWERFUL MICROSCOPE

01:39:45.291 --> 01:39:47.026
AND COULD PEER INTO AN ELECTRON

01:39:47.026 --> 01:39:52.665
I WOULD SEE
A VIBRATING VIOLIN STRING.

01:39:52.665 --> 01:39:54.834
IT CHANGES INTO GRAVITY.

01:39:54.834 --> 01:39:56.569
IT CHANGES INTO LIGHT.

01:39:56.569 --> 01:39:58.304
SO, IN OTHER WORDS

01:39:58.304 --> 01:40:00.906
OUR BODIES ARE NOTHING
BUT COLLECTIONS OF STRINGS.

01:40:00.906 --> 01:40:03.075
AND THE LAWS GOVERNING
THESE STRINGS

01:40:03.075 --> 01:40:05.244
ARE THE HARMONIES
OF THE STRINGS

01:40:05.244 --> 01:40:06.979
AND THEY ARE THE LAWS
OF PHYSICS.

01:40:10.449 --> 01:40:13.486
Osgood:
THEORISTS USUALLY
IMAGINE STRINGS

01:40:13.486 --> 01:40:15.654
AS INCREDIBLY SMALL
CLOSED LOOPS

01:40:15.654 --> 01:40:18.691
MORE LIKE RUBBER BANDS
THAN ANYTHING ELSE.

01:40:18.691 --> 01:40:22.161
ORDINARY MATTER,
EVEN SPACE, TIME AND ENERGY

01:40:22.161 --> 01:40:25.631
ARE NOTHING MORE THAN
THE VIBRATIONS OF STRINGS.

01:40:27.366 --> 01:40:32.137
TO PHYSICISTS THEY ARE
BEAUTIFUL, ELEGANT, SIMPLE--

01:40:32.137 --> 01:40:35.174
EVERYTHING THEY DREAM ABOUT.

01:40:35.174 --> 01:40:36.909
THEN WHEN I INTEGRATE...

01:40:36.909 --> 01:40:40.813
Osgood:
BUT THE MATHEMATICS NEEDED TO
DESCRIBE THEM IS ANYTHING BUT.

01:40:40.813 --> 01:40:42.548
A-B-C-D...

01:40:42.548 --> 01:40:43.849
MY CLAIM IS THAT

01:40:43.849 --> 01:40:46.452
THIS THING I WRITE ON
THIS SIDE OF THE EQUATION

01:40:46.452 --> 01:40:48.621
IS A SUPER-SYMMETRIC DEFINITION
OF AN INDEX

01:40:48.621 --> 01:40:51.657
AND THE STATEMENT IS THAT
THE TOPOLOGY OF THE SUPERSPACE

01:40:51.657 --> 01:40:52.958
CAN ONLY BE GENERATED

01:40:52.958 --> 01:40:55.127
BY THE TOPOLOGY
OF THE BOSONIC MANIFOLD.

01:40:55.127 --> 01:40:58.597
Gates:
MATHEMATICS FOR
A THEORETICAL PHYSICIST

01:40:58.597 --> 01:41:01.200
REALLY IS AN EXTRASENSORY ORGAN.

01:41:01.200 --> 01:41:04.670
I CANNOT MAKE MYSELF
AS SMALL AS AN ATOM;

01:41:04.670 --> 01:41:07.706
I CANNOT MAKE MYSELF
THE SIZE OF A PROTON.

01:41:07.706 --> 01:41:09.441
BUT WITH MATHEMATICS

01:41:09.441 --> 01:41:11.610
I HAVE AN ACCURATE
REPRESENTATION OF THAT

01:41:11.610 --> 01:41:13.345
I HAVE AN ACCURATE
REPRESENTATION OF THAT CAN
USE MY MIND

01:41:13.345 --> 01:41:15.514
TO ACTUALLY LOOK
AT THOSE SMALL THINGS.

01:41:15.514 --> 01:41:16.815
THE FUNNY THING...

01:41:16.815 --> 01:41:19.852
Osgood:
ONE OF THE STRANGEST THINGS
ABOUT STRING THEORY

01:41:20.286 --> 01:41:21.587
IS THAT IT ONLY WORKS

01:41:22.021 --> 01:41:23.756
IF THERE ARE TEN
OR MORE DIMENSIONS.

01:41:23.756 --> 01:41:25.491
CROSS E-8
HETEROTIC THEORY.

01:41:25.491 --> 01:41:28.527
SOME PEOPLE SAY TO US,
"BUT THAT'S NOT COMMONSENSICAL.

01:41:28.527 --> 01:41:29.828
THAT VIOLATES COMMON SENSE."

01:41:30.262 --> 01:41:31.564
WELL, WHY SHOULD COMMON SENSE

01:41:31.564 --> 01:41:33.732
HAVE ANYTHING TO DO
WITH THE UNIVERSE?

01:41:33.732 --> 01:41:36.769
WHY SHOULD THE UNIVERSE
CARE ABOUT YOUR COMMON SENSE?

01:41:36.769 --> 01:41:38.504
SO WE PHYSICISTS ARE PRISONERS.

01:41:38.938 --> 01:41:42.408
WE ARE PRISONERS OF EXPERIMENT,
PRISONERS OF OUR MATHEMATICS

01:41:42.408 --> 01:41:45.010
AND WE SIMPLY GO WHERE
THE MATHEMATICS...

01:41:45.010 --> 01:41:47.179
GO WHERE
THE EXPERIMENTS TAKE US.

01:41:47.179 --> 01:41:49.348
WITH STRING THEORY,
THEY'RE GOING WAY OUT.

01:41:49.348 --> 01:41:51.083
THEY'RE USING MATHEMATICS

01:41:51.517 --> 01:41:54.553
IN A WAY THAT PHYSICISTS HAVE
NEVER USED MATHEMATICS BEFORE.

01:41:54.987 --> 01:41:58.891
IN TEN DIMENSIONS, WE CAN LOOK
AT THE ENTIRE CLIFFORD ALGEBRA

01:41:58.891 --> 01:42:01.060
OF THE DIRAC MATRICES.

01:42:03.662 --> 01:42:05.831
MORE AND MORE ESOTERIC,

01:42:05.831 --> 01:42:08.000
AND, MOST UNFORTUNATELY OF ALL

01:42:08.000 --> 01:42:11.904
FURTHER AND FURTHER REMOVED
FROM EXPERIMENTAL VERIFICATION.

01:42:11.904 --> 01:42:14.506
BUT IN A SENSE,
IT'S THE ONLY GAME IN TOWN.

01:42:14.506 --> 01:42:17.109
IT'S THE ONLY HOPE WE HAVE
OF UNIFYING EVERYTHING.

01:42:17.109 --> 01:42:19.712
WHAT WE ARE TALKING ABOUT NOW

01:42:19.712 --> 01:42:22.748
IS UNDERSTANDING ALL FOUR
FUNDAMENTAL FORCES.

01:42:22.748 --> 01:42:25.351
THAT'S THE POWER OF THIS THEORY.

01:42:25.351 --> 01:42:28.387
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT A THEORY
OF THE UNIVERSE.

01:42:28.387 --> 01:42:30.556
WILL IT GIVE ME BETTER
COLOR TELEVISION?

01:42:30.990 --> 01:42:32.291
THE ANSWER IS NO.

01:42:32.291 --> 01:42:34.893
IT'S NOT GOING TO GIVE YOU
A BIGGER TOASTER.

01:42:34.893 --> 01:42:37.930
IT'S NOT GOING TO GIVE YOU
BETTER SLICED BREAD.

01:42:37.930 --> 01:42:40.532
BUT IT WILL GIVE YOU
IS A THEORY THAT WILL AFFECT

01:42:40.532 --> 01:42:43.135
THE FUTURE COURSE
OF HUMAN CIVILIZATION.

01:42:43.135 --> 01:42:47.906
YOUR
GREAT-GREAT-GREAT-GRANDCHILDREN
WILL ONE DAY LIVE

01:42:47.906 --> 01:42:51.810
TO HARNESS THE POWER
OF THE UNIFIED FIELD THEORY.

01:42:54.413 --> 01:42:57.883
Osgood:
NO ONE KNOWS IF STRING THEORY
IS THE FINAL THEORY

01:42:58.317 --> 01:43:01.787
BUT IF IT ISN'T, PHYSICISTS
ARE SURE TO KEEP SEARCHING.

01:43:07.426 --> 01:43:10.462
Lewin:
I THINK IT'S ALMOST
A RELIGIOUS BELIEF

01:43:10.462 --> 01:43:15.668
THAT THINGS MUST SOMEHOW...
VERY DEEP DOWN BE SIMPLE

01:43:15.668 --> 01:43:20.005
AND THAT WE ARE
TO SOME DEGREE BLIND

01:43:20.005 --> 01:43:23.042
AND DON'T SEE THE SIMPLICITY,
BUT ARE SEARCHING FOR IT.

01:43:25.210 --> 01:43:29.548
NOW, THAT'S WHAT PHYSICS
HAS BEEN DOING ALWAYS--

01:43:29.548 --> 01:43:34.319
VERY DIFFICULT PROCESSES,
VERY DIFFICULT PHENOMENON

01:43:34.319 --> 01:43:38.223
WHICH SEEMINGLY
ARE UNRELATED, CHAOTIC...

01:43:38.223 --> 01:43:42.995
THROUGH SIMPLE DESCRIPTIONS PULL
THEM TOGETHER AND UNIFY THEM.

01:43:42.995 --> 01:43:46.465
AND THAT WILL GO ON
FOR A LONG, LONG TIME.

01:43:51.670 --> 01:43:55.140
Osgood:
ASTRONOMERS WILL ALSO KEEP
TRYING TO SOLVE

01:43:55.140 --> 01:43:57.309
THE MYSTERIES OF THE UNIVERSE.

01:43:57.309 --> 01:43:59.044
ON A MOUNTAIN IN ARIZONA

01:43:59.044 --> 01:44:01.647
TEAM OF SCIENTISTS
ONIS SEARCHING THE SKYNA ONE

01:44:02.081 --> 01:44:04.683
FOR CLUES TO THE ULTIMATE FATE
OF THE COSMOS.

01:44:08.153 --> 01:44:10.756
AT THIS AND OTHER TELESCOPES
AROUND THE WORLD

01:44:10.756 --> 01:44:12.925
THEY'RE MEASURING LIGHT

01:44:12.925 --> 01:44:15.094
FROM STARS HALFWAY ACROSS
THE UNIVERSE.

01:44:16.829 --> 01:44:18.130
AND THIS IS SUPERNOVA...

01:44:18.130 --> 01:44:21.166
Osgood:
THEN, BOB KIRSHNER
AND HIS COLLEAGUES

01:44:21.166 --> 01:44:24.636
USE THOSE MEASUREMENTS
Osgood:
THEN, BOB KIRSHNER
WITH EINSTEIN'S EQUATIONSILL

01:44:24.636 --> 01:44:29.408
TO CALCULATE THE APPROXIMATE
MASS OF THE ENTIRE COSMOS.

01:44:29.408 --> 01:44:32.444
THIS IS NOT EASY.

01:44:38.951 --> 01:44:41.120
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO DO

01:44:41.120 --> 01:44:42.855
EXCEPT JUST SIT THERE
AND TAKE IT.

01:44:45.023 --> 01:44:47.626
Osgood:
IF KIRSHNER FINDS ENOUGH MASS

01:44:47.626 --> 01:44:50.662
IT MEANS THE UNIVERSE
WILL ONE DAY STOP EXPANDING

